  'continuous.notice.manualPause': { 'zh-CN': '监测已由您暂停；暂停时间不会计入持续时长。', 'zh-TW': '監測已由您暫停；暫停時間不會計入持續時間。', en: 'You paused monitoring. Paused time is not included in the duration.' },
